snippet.title: Voice Comms Highlights: Red Bull League of Its Own
snippet.description:
Europe’s finest teams met in Munich to test T1’s League of Legends expertise once again.
Red Bull League of Its Own made its grand return to Germany on November 29th, taking over the SAP Garden in Munich for the third edition of the one-day invitational tournament. The pressure was on this year, as reigning champions T1 returned to the stage along with some of Europe’s most celebrated teams, all going head-to-head in an unmissable end-of-year showdown.
